	<ThingDef ParentName="PlantBase">
    <defName>LoseBambooShoot_Plants</defName>
	<label>迷途笋</label>
		<description>这种竹笋成长飞快,很容易便会形成竹林。

如果是在广阔且地面不平坦的地方形成的竹林,歪斜的竹子和不断变换的景色就会让人失去方向感,即使本来打算直走也会在不觉间回到原处,迷途竹林的称号便是由此而来。

虽然竹笋很美味,但是除了对竹林熟悉的采笋人以外，最好还是不要踏入较好。</description>
		<graphicData>
      <texPath>Plants/LoseBambooShoot_Plants</texPath>
      <graphicClass>Graphic_Random</graphicClass>
        <shadowData>
          <volume>(0.15, 0.3, 0.15)</volume>
          <offset>(0,0,-0.38)</offset>
        </shadowData>
    </graphicData>
    <selectable>true</selectable>
    <statBases>
      <Beauty>2</Beauty>
      <BeautyOutdoors>2</BeautyOutdoors>
      <Nutrition>0.6</Nutrition>
    </statBases>
    <minifiedDef IsNull="True" />
    <ingestible />
    <plant>
      <dieIfLeafless>true</dieIfLeafless>
      <growDays>2</growDays>
      <visualSizeRange>0.8~2.0</visualSizeRange>
      <sowMinSkill>8</sowMinSkill>
      <sowTags>
        <li>Ground</li>
      </sowTags>
      <sowResearchPrerequisites Inherit="False">
        <li>DeepInTheBambooForest</li>
      </sowResearchPrerequisites>
      <topWindExposure>0.15</topWindExposure>
      <mustBeWildToSow>false</mustBeWildToSow>
      <immatureGraphicPath>Plants/LoseBambooShoot_Plants</immatureGraphicPath>
      <harvestWork>200</harvestWork>
      <harvestTag>Standard</harvestTag>
      <forceIsTree>true</forceIsTree>
      <harvestYield>1</harvestYield>
      <harvestedThingDef>LoseBambooShoot</harvestedThingDef>
      <harvestFailable>true</harvestFailable>
    </plant>
